precis:
Amendment to the ATLANTIC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1985 which provides for the
reinstatement of certain provisions concerning lobster fishing {subsections
57(2), (3) and (4)} which were inadvertently omitted in recent revisions
to the Regulations.
